                >AI-powered mental health platform that connects users with licensed therapists through a secure video chat interface. The MVP includes real-time matching algorithm based on user preferences, symptoms, and therapist availability, integrated scheduling system, secure HIPAA-compliant video calls, and automated session notes. Users can browse therapist profiles, read reviews, and book sessions 24/7. The platform addresses the problem of long wait times and limited access to mental health care by making therapy accessible, affordable, and convenient.</textarea>
